{"tid":1277246,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益) 新增識別三毛系統","createTime":"2019-07-02T06:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T07:31:43.000Z","uid":197569,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"af8112e89813bb15aa7f25da2362d1a8c222dcb5","tid":1277246,"uid":197569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"出左個P牌，大家都覺得好有用<br />\n之不過P牌有個漏洞，就係只可以識別新三毛<br />\n而舊三毛呢，大家都仲要忍受佢地既言論<br />\n所以我有以下建議，希望大家討論下WORK唔WORK<br />\n<br />\n第一:整個獨立個人正/負評系統，要禁入去會員版面先可以評既<br />\n第二:開POST既正/負評數唔關個人正/負評數事，以免有啲巴打以後玩唔到假膠POST<br />\n第三:每個人只可以評一個人一次，唔可以瘋狂負評佢，以免三毛利用呢樣野反攻<br />\n第四 P牌唔可以評人地，以免三毛瘋狂開AC反攻<br />\n第五 P牌若果比人負評得多，P牌會extend/沒得甩牌<br />\n<br />\n我相信咁樣可以令到新/舊五毛全部現形<br />\n我地要令佢地永遠單機連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec44b2ab9d5c1dd83174630aa643973375c45c1","tid":1277246,"uid":197569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"046727a77da51d797d7263e2b375e43b5d9c3430","tid":1277246,"uid":197569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17765d2cb6acc2cbc6e507128d19d1e8f3505e5f","tid":1277246,"uid":197569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:48:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96ccb1a9961373f22aeb760875eeaaf9614d408b","tid":1277246,"uid":197569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:49:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a822aa8e7459aa46679cc4c1fd345dbb6b7eeb2d","tid":1277246,"uid":197569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e81461e50dd7bdfb1e68084fc1f134d3d070f48","tid":1277246,"uid":197569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a3c6cc2420bca6ffbc7e57326fce005648b7c21","tid":1277246,"uid":197569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e584